title: Joeyp
author: Joeyp
content: Here is CPU frequency overclocking world records - https://valid.x86.fr/records.htmlAnyone from forum can also share his/her results.This site has also other interesting topics - CPU Cores Distribution, GPU Manufacturers, RAM memory capacity - https://valid.x86.fr/statistics.htmlAnd there is also CPU- Z, free system information software for 32bit and 64bit OS - https://www.cpuid.com/softwares/cpu-z.htmlTip: CPU overclocking can lead to new PC/laptop buying from CPU damage.
